<lyrics>[V1]
 I'm a child of God, I fully belong to Him.
 I may cast all my cares unto Him.
 If I get astray on the road, Jesus shall find the lost lamb,
 He takes him on His shoulders, heals the wounds.

[V2]
 Now I'm on my way home, Jesus showing the way,
 He walks before me, the same light shining.
 The Word tells me this; Look up to the Calvary,
 Everything has been fulfilled for you.

[V3]
 Chorus
 So I run with joy, always trusting in the Lord.
 I know there's a Home in Heaven that awaits for me.
 So I run with joy, always trusting in the Lord.
 I know there's a Home in Heaven that awaits for me.

[V4]
 The Son of God suffered and went into position of a child.
 You got a Father who is in Heaven, if I only believe this,
 the Heaven shall open before me,
 I see the wonderful, holy Lamb.

[V5]
 Jesus loves me, leads me to my Father's Home.
